# The ATOM Token

<HighlightBox type="learning">

The ATOM is the Cosmos Hub's native token. It's is used to secure the network and pay for transaction fees, but has also been the token which has funded development of the Cosmos stack and other projects in the wider ecosystem.

</HighlightBox>

